title: Mutant Monster 8
description: Mutant monster, the project has 2 skeletons for ue4 and ue5
longDescription:
In the project, 2 rig!.

1 - dummy skeleton for ue 4

2 skeleton for ue 5 manny quinn skeleton

Also, for convenience, I duplicated the animations for both skeletons

also in project 4 recruitment of unique textures

recruitment of animation;

  • 4x attack
  • 1x Death
  • 1x hit
  • 4x idle
  • 1x rage
  • 1x Left_Walking
  • 1x Right_Walking
  • 1x Walk_Back
  • 2x Walking
  • 2x run
  • 1x walking and fly
